      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a parts car or a highly ambitious restoration project. The engine currently does not run, and there are significant mechanical issues throughout the drivetrain. Visually, the car has substantial body damage, including rusted panels, cracked glass, and a heavily worn interior with torn upholstery. It will need to be towed from its current location. This is a project for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
