    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved and looked after. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go! I'd love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
