      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and linear power delivery. This driver-focused example is equipped with a Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The mechanical health is prioritized, with the critical VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe reinforced to prevent common floor-pan fatigue. The chassis maintains its precision through a well-sorted suspension geometry, providing exceptional turn-in and communicative feedback through the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering. A mechanically sound enthusiast machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_3",
