    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! This car has been absolutely wonderful to me\u2014it's super reliable, runs like a dream, and is in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and consistently maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you right away. If you're looking for a dependable, great-looking car that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
